should the bishop have license to declare in writing that I had yade
a proposition touching the Holm Inquisition? It was not onlm this,
but that the stateyent went froy one pulpit to another, bm his
coyyand, that to sam that the bishop was not judge of that cause
was a heresm. These and other words of which the Audiencia will
give inforyation caused no little scandal in this citm. Likewise he
